"Our idea is to create a community-driven app that motivates children to engage in regular physical activity by connecting them with peers for group sports and fitness challenges. Kids can form teams, participate in personalized and group challenges, and track their steps and activity levels, receiving rewards for meeting specific goals. This gamified approach makes exercise fun and social, as children earn prizes for reaching step counts and completing various challenges, whether set individually or as a team. By fostering a sense of community, teamwork, and healthy competition, the app encourages kids to embrace a more active and balanced lifestyle."
